{"tid":1392602,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"想放棄","createTime":"2019-07-31T20:27:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T21:08:11.000Z","uid":27813,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"488a44e897faf6fb3e871b31eeb6f59c5bdc68ec","tid":1392602,"uid":27813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T20:27:55.000Z","msg":"凌晨三點鐘<br />\n諗起呢2個月發生嘅事好攰阿 好想放棄<br />\n心諗算啦 到最後未又係輸<br />\n好無力 好嬲但又咩都做唔到 但諗到有好多義士受傷 被人吿可能要坐10年 而我就涼住冷氣係張床度咩事都無 好愧疚 好慚愧阿<br />\n<br />\n上YouTube 輕鬆下唔好係咁諗但成個recommend list都係呢排d野<br />\n一search &ldquo;香港人&rdquo; 之後就睇到呢條片<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/oseSB9CLrnI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FoseSB9CLrnI&d=puaUx2dgpXXsrsLU9noyGG9V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=0cac5f4f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/oseSB9CLrnI</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔係我整嘅 但我睇完之後喊到仆街<br />\n如果邊個呢刻想放棄嘅<br />\n盡情咁喊 發洩完冷靜返好諗下如果你放棄咁d手足點算 係咪想睇住自己屋企淪陷都由佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSorry for 1999<br />\nacc開左好耐但講野唔叻所以無po過咩"},{"pid":"d5cd78ec832630bb6ac28ec814ea0efd99448044","tid":1392602,"uid":164043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T20:28:48.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><br />\n<code>「然遍地腥羶，滿街狼犬！」「吾今日死無餘憾，</code><br />\n<code>國事成不成，自有同志者在。」 - 林覺民 1911</code><br />\n<code>「我哋係前世做錯事 所以今世要搞革命！」</code><br />\n<code>- 無名 2019</code></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光</span>明之子  奮起之<span style=\"color: gold;\">時</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">復</span>赴抗暴   驍勇世<span style=\"color: gold;\">代</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">香</span>城安<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g7qZ3RL.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"ht